Activity1: Create High Priority Lead Email Alert
Steps:
1. In the quick find box, search for email alerts.
2. Click on email alerts
3. Click on Continue
4. Click on New Email Alert
5. Give the Description as High Priority Student Application Email Alert
6. Unique Name will be auto populated
7. Select the object as Student Enrollment
8. Select the High Priority Student Application Notification Email Template
9. For Recipient Type User and Select Student Enrollment Owner
10.Click on Save.

